1. Introduction
Welcome to Rakesh Bhadani Apps. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting the personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our applications. By using our apps, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
2. Information We Collect
Personal Data:
We do not collect any personal data from users.
Face Data:
Our apps may utilize facial recognition technology for certain features (e.g., creating personalized content). However, we do not collect, store, or retain any face data. All facial recognition processes are done on the user’s device, and no face data is transmitted to our servers or third parties.
Third-Party Data Collection:
Our apps use AdMob, a third-party advertising framework, which may collect data. AdMob's data collection and use are governed by their own privacy policies.
3. Use of Your Information
We use the information collected to:
Provide and improve app functionalities.
Display personalized advertisements via AdMob.
Enhance user experience through facial recognition features (if applicable).
4. Disclosure of Your Information
We may share information collected with:
Third-party service providers for advertising purposes.
As required by law, to comply with legal obligations or to protect our rights.
5. Data Security
We implement appropriate security measures to protect your information. However, no electronic transmission or storage method is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
6. Third-Party Websites
Our apps may contain links to third-party websites and services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these third parties. We encourage you to review their privacy policies.
7. Children's Privacy
Our apps are not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children under 13. If we become aware that we have inadvertently collected such data, we will delete it as soon as possible.
8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by updating the "Effective Date" at the top of this policy. Continued use of our apps after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the new policy.
9. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
Email: rakeshapp4@gmail.com
10. Consent
By using our apps, you consent to this Privacy Policy.
